column4: Yeh ek allergic reaction hai jo ke zyada tar skin ki allergy se juda hai. Aapko apne doctor se milna chahiye taake aapka sahi ilaj ho sake. Aapko antihistaminic tablets leni chahiye aur local steroid creams lagani chahiye. Agar yeh behtar nahi hota to aapko apne doctor se milna chahiye.

column3: Mujhe ulti jaisa mehsoos ho raha hai (nausea). kia karun?
column4: Hi, yeh ek aam masla hai jo aksar aise hi shuru hota hai. Aapko apne doctor se milna chahiye aur unse poochna chahiye ke kya aapko koi tests ki zaroorat hai. Aapko shayad ek ECG aur CBC ki zaroorat hogi taake dekha ja sake ke kya aapko koi underlying medical condition hai. Agar aapke doctor ne kuch nahi dikhaya to aapko kuch din tak anti-nausea dawaiyan leni chahiye. Umeed hai yeh madad karega. Khuda hafiz.

column3: Mujhe subah se sar mein dard ho raha hai, koi dawai bataen?
column4: Agar aapko sar mein dard hai to aapko apne doctor se milna chahiye taake wo aapka sahi jaiza le sakein aur aapke liye sahi dawai ka mashwara de sakein. Aapko shayad kisi aur medical masla ka ilaj ki zaroorat ho sakti hai.

column3: Mere bachay ko tez bukhar hai aur wo kuch kha nahi raha.
column4: Mujhe lagta hai ke aapko apne bachay ko doctor ke paas le jana chahiye taake wo jaan sakein ke kya ho raha hai. Agar wo kuch nahi khate to wo shayad dehydrated hain. Aapko apne bachay ko bohot saari fluids deni chahiye, jaise ke paani ya juice. Agar wo kuch nahi khata to aapko usay hospital le jana chahiye taake wo intravenous fluids le sakein. Aapko apne bachay ko bohot saari fluids deni chahiye aur agar wo kuch nahi khata to aapko usay doctor ke paas le jana chahiye.

column3: Mujhe khansi ke sath balgham aa raha hai, kya karoon?
column4: Aapko ek medical provider se milna chahiye taake aapka sahi se jaiza liya ja sake aur ilaj kiya ja sake. Aapko shayad ek chest x-ray ki zaroorat ho sakti hai taake lung infection ko rule out kiya ja sake. Agar aapko infection hai to aapko antibiotics ki zaroorat hogi. Aapko shayad ek expectorant bhi mil sakta hai taake aapki balgham nikal sake. Aapko achi kismet!

column3: Pait mein mror uth rahe hain aur loose motion lage hain.
column4: Aapko apne doctor se milna chahiye taake aapka sahi se jaiza liya ja sake aur diagnosis kiya ja sake.

column3: Mere daant mein shadeed dard hai, dentist ke paas janay tak kya karoon?
column4: Mujhe nahi pata ke kaunsa masla hai, lekin main aapko yeh salah dunga ke aap apne dentist se milain taake aapka sahi jaiza liya ja sake. Aapke daant mein shadeed dard ho sakta hai, lekin yeh bhi ho sakta hai ke aapke kaan mein infection ho raha hai. Yeh dono halatein ek dusre se taluq rakh sakti hain. Aapko is bare mein apne dentist se baat karni chahiye. Umeed hai yeh madad karega.

column3: Mujhe saans lene mein dushwari ho rahi hai jab main sidhiyan charhta hoon.
column4: Aapko ek medical provider se milna chahiye taake aapka sahi se jaiza liya ja sake aur diagnosis kiya ja sake. Aapke sawal ka jawab dena mushkil hai kyunki mujhe aapki medical history ya aapki umar ya jins ka pata nahi hai.

column3: Meri aankhon mein jalan aur pani aa raha hai.
column4: Aapko apne aankhon ke doctor se milna chahiye taake aapka sahi se jaiza liya ja sake. Aapke aankhon mein jalan aur pani aapke bukhar ki wajah se ho sakta hai. Aapko apne aankhon ke doctor se milna chahiye taake aapka sahi se jaiza liya ja sake.

column3: Kaan mein dard hai, shayed paani chala gaya hai.
column4: Hi, main aapko mashwara doonga ke aap apne doctor se milen taake aapka sahi jaiza liya ja sake aur sahi ilaaj diya ja sake. Aapke kaan mein fluid behne ki wajah se ye mumkin hai ke aapke kaan mein paani chala gaya hai. Agar aapka doctor isay confirm kare to aapko ek antibiotic aur ear drops diye jayenge. Aapko achi kismet mile.

column3: Jism par lal nishan par gaye hain aur kharish ho rahi hai.
column4: Hi, mujhe lagta hai ke aapko chickenpox hai. Aapko anti-viral tablets leni chahiye aur agar aapko bukhar hai to aapko Tylenol ya Paracetamol lena chahiye. Agar aapko bukhar nahi hai to aapko sirf Tylenol lena chahiye. Agar aapko bukhar hai to aapko 24 ghante tak Tylenol lena chahiye. Agar aapko bukhar nahi hai to aapko sirf 12 ghante tak Tylenol lena chahiye. Aapko achi kismet!

column3: Mujhe ulti jaisa mehsoos ho raha hai (nausea). kia karun?
column4: Agar aapko ulti jaisa mehsoos ho raha hai to aapko apne doctor se milna chahiye taake wo aapka sahi jaiza le sakein aur aapke liye sahi ilaj de sakein.
